# Build context excludes for the L0 ralph/agent-base build (Dockerfile.agent-base).
# Keeps the context small and — critically — never ships the HOST node_modules/dist into the
# image (node_modules is rebuilt by `npm ci` for the image's own platform; dist is rebuilt by
# `npm run build:daemon`). Only build inputs (package*.json, tsconfig.json, src) are COPYed in.
node_modules
**/node_modules
dist
**/dist
.git
web
.wt
.ralph
.target-repo
*.log
